{"tid":319006,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows Phone 已死！官方宣布暫停系統更新","createTime":"2017-07-12T13:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T15:21:23.000Z","uid":20531,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"720fb0f608303e88f7b9d71ca8d59ad35f52b5f8","tid":319006,"uid":20531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/211429_a98af8468415fb02973827370a2f9595.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F211429_a98af8468415fb02973827370a2f9595.jpg&h=dff6c380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMicrosoft 於 2010 年大力吹捧的自家手機作業系統 Windows Phone ，希望和 iOS 和 Android 一較高下，但拿出來的結果是手機規格普通，系統缺少特色，App 支援更被 iOS 和 Android 大力拋離，最終以手機系統為主 Windows Phone 8.1 就被官方暫停更新，代表著Windows Phone 已死。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/211455_449e7eb58a040a94423da7d5054f778a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F211455_449e7eb58a040a94423da7d5054f778a.jpg&h=d39a1804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然現在有 Windows 10 Mobile，應用上已經著重於 PC 為主設計模式，而且 Windows 10 Mobile 的銷量一般，結果也是一樣。而Windows Phone 8.1 是最後一個手機系統，本應是挽救 Windows Phone 的大更新，但 Windows Phone 7 手機硬件太弱無法升級，失去大批用戶家導致失去App開發者，失去開發者又令用戶進一步的流失，形成惡性循環，完全是回天乏術。所以官方暫停更新也意味著不會再投放資源到手機市場。其實當時 iOS 和 Android 手機兩大系統佔當時市場 9 成份額，Microsoft 想起步已經慢人幾拍，加上和 Nokia 合作推手機更是失利，也只能放棄手機市場。"},{"pid":"24a1240b2ade0e2da8d0fd3f1fe2001cf85ccfc9","tid":319006,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:20:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82f1e1bab1674acc2e7a8b42dec81bedce4e3fc3","tid":319006,"uid":118131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:26:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">完</span></span>"},{"pid":"c77509791827a7cfdccaf9c0c23cd2924090ecbc","tid":319006,"uid":102542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit